## Always guard LLM tests with skip

```typescript
test.skip(
  !process.env.OPENAI_API_KEY && !process.env.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY && !process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY,
  'No LLM API key configured',
);
```

This ensures CI/CD and local runs without API keys don't fail on LLM-dependent tests.
